Name: Kidnapped Girl
About the game: The main character, named Clive, considers himself a psychopath. He has long wanted to hurt someone. So Clive kidnapped a girl on his seventeenth birthday. But the victim was more complicated than he'd thought. A short romantic story with two endings. Game duration: 0,5-2 hours. This game is not suitable for children or those who are easily disturbed. English translation by 'Catherine Chu'
